definitions.definition: A rural community of Halifax Regional Municipality, Nova Scotia , Canada .
A former ghost town in Maricopa County , Arizona , United States , named after Marinette, Wisconsin; Sun City now occupies its old site.
A city , the county seat of Marinette County , Wisconsin , United States . Named after Marie Antoinette Chevalier, an Indian woman.
